.TH OPENPRESS-SERVER 1 "February 2026" "OpenPress 1.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
openpress-server \- The core backend for the OpenPress platform
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B openpress-server
[\fB--port\fR \fIport\fR] [\fB--config\fR \fIfile\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B openpress-server
starts the vibe.d web server, connects to the SQLite database, and serves the API endpoints.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-\-port
Specify the port to listen on (default: 8080).
.TP
.BR \-\-config
Path to the JSON configuration file.
.SH SEE ALSO
openpress.conf(5)
